Chairman


Address
1 Robert Rich WayBuffalo, NY 14213-1701USA+1 716-878-8000 (Phone)716-878-8008 (Fax)

Website links


www.richscatering.com










Starting in 1945 with "the miracle cream from the soya bean," Rich Products has grown from a niche maker of soy-based whipped toppings and frozen desserts to a global US frozen foods maker. The family-owned business has developed other products, such as toppings and icings, and Coffee Rich (nondairy coffee creamer). It has expanded its product line to include frozen bakery and pizza doughs and ingredients for the food service and in-store bakery markets, plus appetizers, baked goods, seafood, meatballs, and barbecue meat. Rich Products markets more than 2,000 frozen food items that are sold in more than 110 countries; it has kitchens and bakeries around the world, including about 50 locations on six continents.


