Insider Activity


Individual




Melinda R. Rich



Ms. Melinda R. Rich is Independent Director at M&T Bank Corp., President at Rich Entertainment Group, and a Director-Wellness Institute Leadership Council at The Cleveland Clinic Foundation. She is on the Board of Directors at M&T Bank Corp., Rich Products Corp., The Culinary Institute of America, Rich Family Foundation, The Dream Catcher Foundation, Don Hawley Foundation, Erie Canal Harbor Development Corp., National Foundation for Celiac Awareness, Manufacturers & Traders Trust Co., Rich Products of Canada Ltd., and Rock & Roll Hall of Fame & Museum, Inc.
Ms. Rich also served on the board at William Wrigley Jr. Co.
She received her undergraduate degree from The University of Colorado.



